the possessors ( french : les grandes familles ) is a 1958 french drama film directed by denys de la patellière , starring jean gabin , pierre brasseur , bernard blier , jean desailly , françoise christophe and annie ducaux . it tells the story of an industrial and newspaper tycoon and his sons . the screenplay is based on the novel les grandes familles by maurice druon , which won the prix goncourt in 1948 . the film recorded 4,042,041 admissions in france . gabin received the 1959 david di donatello for best foreign actor .